### Example CSS Animation

```css
.wheel-and-hamster {
  transition: all 1s ease-in-out infinite;
  transform: rotate(360deg);
}

.hamster {
  animation: run infinite linear;
}

@keyframes run {
  0% {
    transform: translate(35%,-35%);
  }
  100% {
    transform: translate(35%,35%);
  }
}

